 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/supergrass@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/supergrass@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/supergrass@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/supergrass@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/supergrass">Supergrass</a>分享了新的美国巡回演唱会的细节，并庆祝“我应该可可”成立30周年。找到下面的详细信息，以及其经典曲目“ Alright”的新<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kelly-clarkson">凯利·克拉克森（Kelly Clarkson）</a>的封面。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/supergrass-gaz-coombes-interview-i-should-coco-30-years-anniversary-tour-oasis-britpop-3796303">超级草：“当您回顾一下Britpop的小伙子文化和混乱时，我们不是其中的一部分”</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p>新公告是在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gaz-coombes">Gaz Coombes</a> and Co之后的。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/supergrass-announce-i-should-coco-30th-anniversary-tour-tickets-2025-3794055">分享去年英国巡回演唱会的细节</a>，这将使他们与其他一些粉丝的最爱一起演奏备受赞誉的首张专辑。</p><p>成员们开始<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/supergrass-are-teasing-a-new-announcement-coming-next-week-3793415">取笑在线卷土重来</a>后，新闻发布了，并宣布了格拉斯哥，诺丁汉，谢菲尔德，纽卡斯尔，伯明翰，卡迪夫，利兹和伦敦的巡回演出日期。贝德福德公园（Bedford Park）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/supergrass-add-margate-show-to-i-should-coco-30th-anniversary-tour-with-the-coral-and-jake-bugg-3813157">哈利法克斯（</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/supergrass-add-two-shows-summer-2025-uk-anniversary-tour-buy-tickets-3816377">Halifax）的作品大厅共享了额外的日期</a>，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/supergrass-2025-i-should-coco-anniversary-ludlow-castle-show-buy-tickets-3811637">在卢德洛城堡（Ludlow Castle）的演出</a>。</p><p>现在，乐队宣布他们将在今年晚些时候将巡回演出带到海外 - 确认了六个新约会。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DGOMZR0Nze5/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-versi